OL,6,FA father and son have been handed a
OL,7,Fcombined sentenced of nearly 13 years
OL,8,Fin prison for their part in a complex
OL,9,Fdrug conspiracy.
OL,11,FAnthony Peers, 67, was jailed for four
OL,12,Fyears and six months alongside his 37-
OL,13,Fyear-old son, also called Anthony
OL,14,FPeers, who received an eight year and
OL,15,Fthree month sentence.
