OL,6,FAntony Peers Jr. went by "Tubbyfern"
OL,7,Fon Encrochat, where he communicated
OL,8,Fwith others and organised the
OL,9,Facquisition and supply of cocaine and
OL,10,Fcannabis.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, his father would use a
OL,13,Fhydraulic press to mix and re-press
OL,14,Fblocks of cocaine in his garage on
OL,15,FNorth Lane in Astley.
OL,17,FOn 16 March 2023, Greater Manchester
OL,18,FPolice officers executed five search
OL,19,Fwarrants and arrested the pair.
